name: complex_with_bound_min_max_sum_through_do
section: binding-order
args: a:Int b:Int setup:Bool
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Min/max decomposition of a pair must survive with binding and do sequencing.
law: (= (with [lo (fuzz-min {a} {b}) hi (fuzz-max {a} {b})] (do {setup} (fuzz-add lo hi))) (fuzz-add {a} {b}))
